Are you accusing the others of a mistake?
If your work is not done for the deadline, you forget to send a mail or an important message, do not accuse anyone for this oversight!
Don't put it on account of any chaos in the office or your noisy colleagues!
Recognize it if you have made a mistake and if it has caused inconvenience to others, fix the mistake!
Ask how you can fix your fault, fix negligence!
Do you feel too home at the office?
Putting a jogging and slippers is comfortable at home but they are not suitable for the office!
Do not put on comfortable jogging even if your function allows it!
Don't be neglected, respect your colleagues and yourself by dressing properly, and if your job requires it by putting on pretty and elegant clothes, to go to work!
